{"type":"message","id":"88fc537d","parentId":"affea24e","timestamp":"2026-04-13T07:08:09.639Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Mon 2026-04-13 15:08 GMT+8] 优缺点"}],"timestamp":1776064089631}}
{"type":"message","id":"06b92a0a","parentId":"88fc537d","timestamp":"2026-04-13T07:08:33.764Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants a comparison of the two approaches: built-in hook mechanism vs. plugin system.","thinkingSignature":"cb9a55d385095e13c70e084eb20bd540e7139a08b9a6d22241af750a363fc780"},{"type":"text","text":"\n**方案对比：**\n\n| | 内置 hook 机制 | 插件系统 |\n|---|---|---|\n| **配置方式** | 在 `config.json` 的 `hooks.internal.entries` 声明 | 打包成 npm 包，发布到 clawhub，用命令安装 |\n| **灵活性** | 受限于 `bootstrapFiles` 数组操作 | 可以做任意事情（自定义事件、API 调用等） |\n| **复用性** | 只在当前部署生效 | 可在不同实例间复用，发布后其他人也能用 |\n| **维护成本** | 低，直接改文件 | 需要版本管理、发布流程 |\n| **复杂度** | 简单，改完重启 Gateway 生效 | 重，需要写 SKILL.md、package.json、发布流程 |\n\n**结论：**\n\n你的需求（注入 MEMORY.md + session summary）属于**轻量的一次性定制**，用内置 hook 机制就够了。改动最小，一条配置搞定。\n\n插件系统适合那种需要跨实例复用、或者功能复杂到值得独立维护的场景。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":54,"output":228,"cacheRead":82082,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":82364,"cost":{"input":0.0000162,"output":0.0002736,"cacheRead":0.004924919999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.005214719999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776064089651,"responseId":"062bc95ab71b7887ded9c90dba99001d"}}
